* Yuriy Bilonog disqualified for using drugs according to IOC Executive Board decision of 5. December 2012. The reallocation of the medals is published in IOC Press Releases of 30. December 2012. 




Men's Shot put - Athletics - Athens 2004 Summer Olympics
Event Format:
     
     Athletes competed in a qualifying round followed by the final. Top twelve and ties in the qualifying round and all those reaching the announced qualification limit advanced to the final. In the final all finalists were given three tries. The top eight were then given three more. Event facts: Men's Shot put competition was held at the Olympic Stadium and 39 athletes participated in the event. 





These results for Men's Shot put - Athens 2004 Summer Olympics - are based on the official olympic reports and the Olympian Database
